--tworzenie użydkowika na którym testuje kod i nadanie mu uprawnień polecenia wykonuje będąc zalogowanym na użydkownika system

create user restaurant identified by 123;

GRANT CREATE SESSION TO restaurant;
GRANT UNLIMITED TABLESPACE TO restaurant;
GRANT CREATE TABLE TO restaurant;
GRANT CREATE SEQUENCE TO restaurant;
GRANT CREATE VIEW TO restaurant;
GRANT CREATE TYPE TO restaurant;
GRANT CREATE PROCEDURE TO restaurant;
GRANT CREATE TRIGGER TO restaurant;
GRANT ADMINISTER DATABASE TRIGGER TO restaurant;
GRANT EXECUTE ON DBMS_SCHEDULER TO restaurant;
GRANT CREATE JOB TO restaurant;
